  "body": "> For the final output only (ie. not intermediate outputs), if the output is less than 32 bytes, right-zero-pad it to 32 bytes.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/ebc136a3bdfa6a07b1db7ba44f622683475bdacd/specs/simple-serialize.md#tree-hash\r\n\r\nThis probably deserves being firmed up a bit, so we agree on the same padding, for example when fixing #273",
